title: I'm missing my ranked icons
body: i have been playing since 2014 and recently my silver/bronze and gold ranked icons have disappeared from my icons did i miss some change or something?

replies.body:
Nope they should still be there. They'll be pretty far down though. 

If you still can't find them send in a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)
